WEBVTT

00:08:58.588 --> 00:09:01.611
And my answer is no,

00:09:01.635 --> 00:09:05.663
because they don't like
that particular decision,

00:09:05.687 --> 00:09:08.176
but they don't want to change the system.

00:09:08.200 --> 00:09:10.027
And one of the reasons is because

00:09:10.051 --> 00:09:13.554
they have never, ever
known another system.

00:09:13.578 --> 00:09:16.119
This is the system they know how to work.

00:09:17.516 --> 00:09:19.457
HW: What is wok-throwing, Huang?

00:09:19.481 --> 00:09:24.530
HH: Oh, wok-throwing is when
you blame somebody else.

00:09:24.554 --> 00:09:30.387
Basically, someone who is responsible
in a slang Chinese